      "text": "On June 15th, apartment buildings in Toronto will finally begin to display colour-coded RentSafe signs, backed by the city being able to use remedial action or financial penalties if landlords don’t maintain safe and healthy homes for their tenants-holding corporate landlords to account, ensuring…",
