    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mnhkpfmg7c2c",
      "text": "Access to drinking water, especially when you’re outside in the heat, should be a right no matter where you are in Toronto. Health & safety is simply more important than FIFA restricting fans to buy Coke products. I’ll be asking city hall to push back on this latest greedy & unreasonable FIFA demand",
