    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mngmz3qgc224",
      "text": "I disagree with the TTC’s decision to install barrier fences on subway platforms. I’m convinced it’s a waste of money, and won’t effectively prevent tragedies, trespassing onto the tracks or reduce delays. I support working toward installing real platform edge doors. www.cbc.ca/news/canada/...",
