    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mn7x3422ek26",
      "text": "The Toronto Port Authority is holding their AGM on June 11th. I read their Financial Statements - and they raise big red flags about their hasty support of Doug Ford’s plan to bring jets to Billy Bishop Airport: 1) Ridership is down at Billy Bishop…",
