    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mn7vgnpou226",
      "text": "Too many renters in Toronto are overheating in their own homes. And year after year, they’ve asked city hall for action. It’s time to move forward with a Maximum Temperature By-law to protect the health and safety of our city’s tenants. www.cbc.ca/news/canada/...",
      "author": "Josh Matlow",
      "handle": "joshmatlow.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1780310538,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/joshmatlow.bsky.social/post/3mn7vgnpou226",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mmzh6v5jfk26",
      "text": "Thank you to CHIN Radio for sharing the stories of Toronto’s many cultures, and celebrating the communities that call our city home, for 60 years! And to Lenny Lombardi, Grace Fusillo-Lombardi, their family and staff who proudly continue the late Johnny Lombardi’s legacy.",
